Lola Dueñas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lola_Due%C3%B1as 0 María Dolores Dueñas Navarro (Madrid, 6 October 1971) better known as Lola Dueñas is a Spanish actress. Since 2002, she has worked regularly with the director Pedro Almodóvar. She is the daughter of Nicolás Dueñas and studied in the Teatro de La Abadía of Madrid.
